# ESLint Autofix Workflow

- **Always use ESLint auto-fix** to correct lint issues, especially import sorting. Do not sort imports manually.

## Single file fixes

Run from the repository root:

```bash
yarn eslint <path-to-file> --fix
```

Example:

```bash
yarn eslint clients/extension/src/inpage/providers/ethereum.ts --fix
```

## Multiple files

If your changes affect multiple files, run from the repository root:

```bash
yarn lint:fix
```
